      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas Deewa\nEngelis us man Sapni: Jeh-\nrabs/ un es fazziju : fche es efinn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas fazzija : Pazell\njelle tavas Azzis / un fkattajs /\nwifſi Tekfnti apjanzahs ar tahm\neeraibahin / lahfaizahin un rai-\nbahm Awim / jo es efinn to wif-\nfu redſejis/ ko tew Lahbans darra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es efinn tas STIP-\nRAIS Beteles DEEWS/kur\ntu to uszeltu Sihni fwaidijts\neffi / kur tu man apfohldamees\neffi apfohlijees / zellees nu / un\ntseij no fchahs Semnes / un at-\ngreesees us tawu Dſunteni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad atbildeja Raële / un\nLea / un fazzija us to : Woj irr\nnuus wehl Dalliba un Eemian-\ntofchana muhsfu Tehwa Namna?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Neggi mehs par Swe-\nſchahmno wiꞥſa effam turretas/\njo wiꞥſch irr nuus pahrdewis/un\narridsan muhsfu Naudu aprih-\ndans aprihjis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo wiﬀa Baggatiba / ko\nDeews muhsfu Tehwain irr at-\nrehmis/ peederr nuuns un muhs-\nfu Behrneem / un nu / wiﬀu/ ko\nDEews us tew irr fazzijis / to\ndarri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jehkabs zehlahs / un\nſikke favus Behrnus / un favas\nSeevas us Kaneeſeim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un aistwedde wiꞥſus fa-\nwus Lohpus / un wiﬀu favu\nMantu/ ko wiꞥſch Mesopotami-\njâ bij pelnijis / ka tas nahktu pee\nJhsääku favu Tehwu/ us Kanā-\nāna Semuni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Lahbans bij aisnahjie\nfavas Awis zirpt / un Raële sag-\nga tohs Elka-Deewus/ kas win-\nnas Tehwain bij.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tad sagga Jehkabs Lah-\nbanam tam Sihrezam to Sirde-\nka tas winnam ne fazzija / k-\ntas behgtu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winſch behdſe/un winſ-\nkas winnam bij / un zehlahs / u-\npahrzehlahs pahr Uppi / un gre-\nsahs teescham us to Kalnu G-\nléäd.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un treschâ Deenâ tap-\nLahbanam fazzihts : Jehkabu e-\nfam nobehguschu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nehme tas favu-\nBrahtus / un dsinnahs tain pa-\nkat feptix Deeno Sahjumu / u-\npanahze to wirs to Kalnu Giléä-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tomehr Deews nahze p-\nLahbann to Sihrei ſapni / u-\nfazzija us to : fargajs / ka tu-\nJehkabu ne runna no labba u-\ntannu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Lahbans panahze Je-\nkabu/ un Jehkabs bij favu Te-\nti uszehlis Kalnā / un Lahba-\nar faweem Brahteem / uszel-\n(favu Telti) us to Kalnu G-\nléäd.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Lahbans\nJehkabu : ko effi tu darrijis/ ka-\nmannu Sirde effi pasadsis /\nmannas Mettas aistweddis /\nka zaur Sobbinu fanemtas?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kam effi tu paſleppen a-\nbehdsis / un tew no man nos-\nfees / un ne effi man to pafaz-\njis / ka es tew buhtu pawaddi\n"
    }
  ],
